<br>
I'm still forming my opinion on this service, but I'm leaning towards negative for three reasons:<br>
<br>
1) It will allow folks with a bad reputation to easily wreak more havoc by getting a new name. Unsuspecting folks won't know to be on the lookout for this jerk cause he's got a new handle.<br>
<br>
2) It will allow folks to ebay their characters even easier now, as it will be a cinch to just get a new name once they've purchased their account. Those of us who work hard to level up our charactes won't know what hit them the first time some bought character zaps us!<br>
<br>
